_sText:
Although some prefabs were from the beta 1 i released this is a totally different map, but with the same name.

Already server tested, some people loved it, some people liked it, some people hated it, whatever you decide its another zombie map to play and have fun on :)

Features - 

Barricade rooms
ANTI GRAVITY ROOM (quite good fun ^^)
Camping spots
etc etc

Give it a go, feedback (good or bad, but please constructive) always welcome.

Note to VS3, thanks for allowing the live test, this map is slighty different than the one you have in the placement of spawn points, ive moved them so that round starts dont cause server lag.
